Enum scrypto::prelude::ScryptoCustomTypeKind

pub enum ScryptoCustomTypeKind {
    Reference,
    Own,
    Decimal,
    PreciseDecimal,
    NonFungibleLocalId,
}
Expand description

A schema for the values that a codec can decode / views as valid
